translation[15]{c,v,t}:
  36,13,Inhein misaal ke taur par us basti walon ka qissa sunao jabke usmein Rasool aaye thay
  36,14,Humne unki taraf do Rasool bheje aur unhon ne dono ko jhutla diya phir humne teesra madad ke liye bheja aur unsab ne kaha “Hum tumhari taraf Rasool ki haisiyat se bheje gaye hain”
  36,15,"Basti walon ne kaha “ tum kuch nahin ho magar hum jaise chandh Insaan, aur khuda e rehman ne hargiz koi cheez nazil nahin ki hai, tum mehaz jhoot boltey ho.”"
  36,16,Rasoolon ne kaha “ hamara Rubb jaanta hai ke hum zarooor tumhari taraf Rasool bana kar bheje gaye hain
  36,17,Aur humpar saaf saaf paigham pahuncha dene ke siwa koi zimmedari nahin hai”
  36,18,"Basti waley kehne lagey “hum to tumhein apne liye faal-e-badd (manhoos) samajhte hain , agar tum baaz na aaye to hum tumko sangsaar(stoning) kar dengey aur humse tum badi dardnaak saza paogey”"
  36,19,"Rasoolon ne jawab diya “tumhari faal-e-badd (nahusat) to tumhare apne saath lagi hui hai , kya yeh baatein tum isliye karte ho ke tumhein naseehat ki gayi? Asal baat yeh hai ke tum hadd se guzre huey log ho”"
  36,20,"Itne mein shehar ke door daraaz goshey se ek shaks daudta hua aaya aur bola “Aey meri qaum ke logon, Rasoolon ki pairwi ikhtiyar karlo"
  36,21,Pairwi karo un logon ki jo tumse koi ajar nahin chahte aur theek raaste par hain
  36,22,Aakhir kyun na main us hasti ki bandagi karoon jisne mujhey paida kiya hai aur jiski taraf tum sabko palat kar jana hai
  36,23,Kya main usey chodh kar dusre ko mabood bana loon? Halaanke agar khuda e Rehman mujhey koi nuksaan pahunchana chahe to na unki shafaat mere kisi kaam aa sakti hai aur na woh mujhey chuda hi sakte hain
  36,24,Agar main aisa karoon to main sareeh gumraahi mein mubtala ho jaunga
  36,25,"Main to tumhare Rubb par iman le aaya, tum bhi meri baat maan lo.”"
  36,26,(aakhir e kaar un logon ne usey qatal kardiya aur) us shaks se kehdiya gaya ke “daakhil ho ja jannat mein” usne kaha “kaash meri qaum ko maaloom hota
  36,27,Ke mere Rubb ne kis cheez ki badaulat meri magfirat farma di aur mujhey ba-izzat logon mein daakhil farmaya”